entries.title_d: Hunt down the Black Sun's hired thugs
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Hidden Dagger Executioner
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 We have an Imperial prison shuttle traveling through the area requesting escort.  The Hidden Daggers have been targeting them recently, so stay alert. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_target_d: A mercenary in an old band of Assassins
entries.quest_escort_d: Must destroy these targets to complete the mission
entries.failed_escape: You have failed the mission because the target escaped.
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Primary objective destroyed, finish off remaining escort. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 Nice shooting, that Hidden Dagger assassins group is no more.
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 Try not to underestimate them Captain, the Hidden Daggers are professionals. \#pcontrast3 >
